title: EASEUS Photo Recovery 2.1.1
description:
EASEUS Photo Recovery is an easy to use software utility that enables you to recover your photos, videos and music from your local computer or removable devices. No matter multimedia files have been deleted accidently, memory card has been formatted or corrupted, or even the media files missing with unknown reasons, you can get these files back with EASEUS Photo Recovery easily.

The multimedia file types EASEUS Photo Recovery supported are:
Image: JPG, JPEG, GIF, BMP, TIFF, PNG
Audio: MP3, WMA, WMV, MID, AIF
Video: MOV, AVI, MPG, RM, 3GP, MP4


5.9 MB / Windows 2K / XP / 2003 / Vista
